---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Text Blog">
	<h1>About</h1>
	<p>This is a simple, text-focused blog created with Astro. The focus is on content and readability, without unnecessary distractions.</p>
	
	<h2>Why Text Blog?</h2>
	<p>In a world full of flashy websites and endless distractions, sometimes we need to go back to basics. This blog emphasizes:</p>
	
	<ul>
		<li>Clean typography</li>
		<li>Fast loading times</li>
		<li>Excellent readability</li>
		<li>Focus on content</li>
	</ul>
</Layout>

<style>
	ul {
		margin: 1rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}
	li {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}
</style>